///How to Product Research for CPA Marketing//////////////

Step-1
Login CPA Network
-	Open browser
-	Login to a CPA Network 
-	Click on “Offer”
-	Search by “United States”

Step-2
Check Offer Product in Google Trends
-	Copy a product name from offer list
-	Go to Google Trends
-	In search box: product name
-	Country: United States
-	Past Day: 90 Days
-	From Line Graph Section, download data in excel file
-	Open excel file, select all numbers  Σ Auto Sum  Average 
-	Open an excel and write below way

Product Name		Avg. Value
-----------------------------------------------
Abc			        39.16
Bcd			        24.08

Step-3
Compare Multiple Offer Product
-	In excel, short the “Avg. Value” (Big to Small)
-	Mark top products that have value more than 35

Step-4
Set Product Type (Ever Green product, Seasonal Product)
-	Mark product as Type
-	We will work only “Ever Green Product”

Step-5
Don’t work for below product offer (Seasonal Product)
-	Christmas Product Offer
-	Black Friday Product Offer

-	New Year Product Offer

